---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Last updated: October 3, 2025</p>
      
      <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
      <p>
        Real & Raw Gospel respects your privacy. We are committed to protecting any personal information you share with us.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        Currently, this website does not collect personal information unless you voluntarily provide it (e.g., through contact forms or newsletter signups if implemented in the future).
      </p>
      
      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We do not currently use any analytics or tracking services. If we implement privacy-respecting analytics in the future, we will update this policy accordingly.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This website may use essential cookies for basic functionality (e.g., remembering your Bible reader preferences). We do not use tracking cookies.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>
        Our website may contain links to third-party websites (e.g., affiliate book links, video platforms). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        We take reasonable measures to protect any information you provide. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our website is intended for general audiences and does not knowingly collect information from children under 13.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us through the information provided on our website.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

